{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_story.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You</strong> wake up as a ghost, with no memory of who you were or how you died. The only clue to your past is the <strong>empty suit of armour you now possess</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore an abandoned castle and piece together your memories, you\u2019ll uncover your tale: A tale of broken promises, regret, and bonds that last beyond death.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But your story doesn\u2019t have to die with you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>How will you write its ending?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_snow.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/screenshot-gif-2-sm.gif?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_snow.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_feat.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Last Winter Knight</i> is an <strong>atmospheric fantasy</strong> <strong>visual novel</strong> that features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\tA <strong>melancholy story</strong> where you play as a ghostly knight haunting a suit of armour.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\t<strong>Point and click</strong> segments that let you explore a lonely castle.* </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\t<strong>Hand-crafted artwork</strong> that captures a dark fairy tale feel. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\tA <strong>pensive piano soundtrack</strong> that subtly shifts depending on where and what you examine. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\t<strong>Multiple endings</strong> to uncover: Will you remained trapped in your armour, or finally find peace?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>*Accessibility note:</strong> Instead of clicking, you can hover over objects and hit -Enter- to interact with them. Text can be advanced with -Space- </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_snow.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/screenshot-gif-1b.gif?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_snow.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_cred.png?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a solo project with art, music, story, programming and sound design by ENDYSIS (me!) Thank you so much for checking out my game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special thank you to Wanpans Armoury for providing armour foley  and Sammy L. for moral support.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/mirror-gif.gif?t=1735444194\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768420/extras/st_snow.png?t=1735444194\" /></p>","background":"h